---

<BaseLayout
  title="Travel Agency Partners | Go Kilimanjaro Treks"
  description="Build a profitable Tanzania programme with a direct Moshi-based ground operator. Net rates, marketing assets, and dedicated partner support from Nelson Mushi and the Go Kilimanjaro Treks team."
  ogImage="https://gokilimanjarotreks.com/images/og-kilimanjaro.jpg"
  ogImageAlt="Travel agency partnership programme with Go Kilimanjaro Treks in Moshi, Tanzania"
  schemas={schemas}
>
  <main>
<section class="partners-hero">
  <img src="/images/hero.jpg" alt="" aria-hidden="true" class="partners-hero-bg" loading="eager" fetchpriority="high">
  <div class="container">
    <span class="partners-hero-eyebrow">For Travel Agencies &amp; Tour Operators</span>
    <h1>Build a Profitable <em>Tanzania</em> Programme.</h1>
    <p class="lead">Partner with a Moshi-based ground operator who has been on the mountain for over two decades. Strong commercial terms, dedicated partner support from Nelson personally, and on-the-ground operational quality your clients will write home about.</p>
    <div class="partners-hero-cta">
      <a href="contact.html?subject=Partnership%20enquiry" class="btn-gold">Schedule a Call With Nelson &#x2192;</a>
      <a href="https://wa.me/255677917500?text=Hi%20Nelson%2C%20I%27d%20like%20to%20discuss%20a%20travel%20agency%20partnership." class="btn-line" target="_blank" rel="noopener">&#x1F4AC; WhatsApp Nelson</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="partner-stats">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="partner-stats-grid">
      <div class="partner-stat"><div class="partner-stat-num">22+</div><div class="partner-stat-label">Years On The Mountain</div></div>
      <div class="partner-stat"><div class="partner-stat-num">270+</div><div class="partner-stat-label">Personal Summits</div></div>
      <div class="partner-stat"><div class="partner-stat-num">100%</div><div class="partner-stat-label">Safety Record</div></div>
      <div class="partner-stat"><div class="partner-stat-num">24h</div><div class="partner-stat-label">Quote Turnaround</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section style="padding:90px 0;background:var(--white)">
  <div class="container">
    <span class="section-eyebrow-center">Why Partner With Us</span>
    <h2 class="section-title-center">A Genuine <em>Partner</em>, Not Just a Vendor.</h2>
    <p class="section-lead-center">We sit in Moshi at the foot of the mountain. We answer our own email. We guide the climbs we sell to your clients. The result is a partnership that actually behaves like one.</p>
    <div class="value-grid">
<div class="value-card"><div><svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.7"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3 13.125C3 12.504 3.504 12 4.125 12h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125v6.75C7.5 20.496 6.996 21 6.375 21h-2.25A1.125 1.125 0 013 19.875v-6.75zM9.75 8.625c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125v11.25c0 .621-.504 1.125-1.125 1.125h-2.25a1.125 1.125 0 01-1.125-1.125V8.625zM16.5 4.125c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h2.25C20.496 3 21 3.504 21 4.125v15.75c0 .621-.504 1.125-1.125 1.125h-2.25a1.125 1.125 0 01-1.125-1.125V4.125z"/></svg></div><h3>Strong Commercial Terms</h3><p>Net pricing that lets your agency build a healthy margin without inflating retail. Transparent tiered rates that improve as your booking volume grows.</p></div>
<div class="value-card"><div><svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.7"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5"/></svg></div><h3>Direct Operator Relationship</h3><p>No middlemen between you and the team running the climb. You quote with confidence because the person guiding your client is on the other end of this email.</p></div>
<div class="value-card"><div><svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.7"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75M21 12c0 1.268-.63 2.39-1.593 3.068a3.745 3.745 0 01-1.043 3.296 3.745 3.745 0 01-3.296 1.043A3.745 3.745 0 0112 21c-1.268 0-2.39-.63-3.068-1.593a3.746 3.746 0 01-3.296-1.043 3.745 3.745 0 01-1.043-3.296A3.745 3.745 0 013 12c0-1.268.63-2.39 1.593-3.068a3.745 3.745 0 011.043-3.296 3.745 3.745 0 013.296-1.043A3.745 3.745 0 0112 3c1.268 0 2.39.63 3.068 1.593a3.746 3.746 0 013.296 1.043 3.746 3.746 0 011.043 3.296A3.745 3.745 0 0121 12z"/></svg></div><h3>Sell With Confidence</h3><p>Twenty-two years on the mountain, 270-plus summits to Uhuru Peak, WFR-certified guides, and a 100 percent safety record. Brochure-grade credentials with the receipts to back them.</p></div>
<div class="value-card"><div><svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.7"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3.75 13.5l10.5-11.25L12 10.5h8.25L9.75 21.75 12 13.5H3.75z"/></svg></div><h3>24-Hour Quote Turnaround</h3><p>Custom itineraries and quotes back to you within one business day. Same-day response on most queries. Your client never waits.</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="why-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="why-grid">
      <div class="why-text">
        <span class="section-eyebrow">Built On the Mountain</span>
        <h2>Why Your Clients Will <em>Summit</em>.</h2>
        <p>Nelson grew up in the Machame ward at the foot of Kilimanjaro and has guided eight routes on the mountain over twenty-two years. He helped pioneer the Karanga to Barafu Camp shortcut that operators now use across the Southern Circuit. He has personally summited Uhuru Peak over 270 times.</p>
        <p>That depth of experience is what your client is buying when they book through your agency. We are not adding ourselves to your catalogue. We are giving you a credible answer to every safety, fitness, and itinerary question your sales team gets asked.</p>
        <div class="why-checks">
          <div class="why-check"><svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg><div><strong>WFR-Certified Senior Guides</strong><span>Wilderness First Responder credential on every senior guide. Twice-daily pulse oximetry on every climb.</span></div></div>
          <div class="why-check"><svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg><div><strong>Porter Welfare Standards</strong><span>Above-minimum porter wages, safe load limits, proper kit, and proper sleeping conditions on every climb. Ethical sourcing your clients can be proud of.</span></div></div>
          <div class="why-check"><svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg><div><strong>KCMC Hospital Partnership</strong><span>Direct rescue relationships with Kilimanjaro Christian Medical Centre and KiliMedAir helicopter service. Documented evacuation protocols.</span></div></div>
          <div class="why-check"><svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg><div><strong>Full E-E-A-T Documentation</strong><span>Credentials, safety protocols, route information, FAQs. Your due-diligence team can verify everything we claim.</span></div></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="why-photo">
        <img src="/images/nelson.jpg" alt="Nelson Mushi, lead guide and partnership contact at Go Kilimanjaro Treks">
        <div class="why-badge">
          <div class="h">Your Contact</div>
          <div class="t">Nelson Mushi</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="provide-section">
  <div class="container">
    <span class="section-eyebrow-center">What Partners Get</span>
    <h2 class="section-title-center">Everything You Need to <em>Sell Tanzania</em>.</h2>
    <p class="section-lead-center">The tools, terms, and operational support that make selling a Go Kilimanjaro Treks programme easier than selling alternatives. Built for agency reality, not marketing slides.</p>
    <div class="provide-grid">
<div class="provide-card"><div><svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.7"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19.5 14.25v-2.625a3.375 3.375 0 00-3.375-3.375h-1.5A1.125 1.125 0 0113.5 7.125v-1.5a3.375 3.375 0 00-3.375-3.375H8.25m0 12.75h7.5m-7.5 3H12M10.5 2.25H5.625c-.621 0-1.125.504-1.125 1.125v17.25c0 .621.504 1.125 1.125 1.125h12.75c.621 0 1.125-.504 1.125-1.125V11.25a9 9 0 00-9-9z"/></svg></div><h3>Tailored Itineraries</h3><p>Every quote built specifically for your client's group size, fitness level, dates, and goals. Northern Circuit for clients who want highest summit odds. Rongai for wet-season departures. Lemosho 8-day as the workhorse. We know which fits each profile.</p></div>
<div class="provide-card"><div><svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.7"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15 19.128a9.38 9.38 0 002.625.372 9.337 9.337 0 004.121-.952 4.125 4.125 0 00-7.533-2.493M15 19.128v-.003c0-1.113-.285-2.16-.786-3.07M15 19.128v.106A12.318 12.318 0 018.624 21c-2.331 0-4.512-.645-6.374-1.766l-.001-.109a6.375 6.375 0 0111.964-3.07M12 6.375a3.375 3.375 0 11-6.75 0 3.375 3.375 0 016.75 0zm8.25 2.25a2.625 2.625 0 11-5.25 0 2.625 2.625 0 015.25 0z"/></svg></div><h3>Dedicated Partner Contact</h3><p>Nelson personally handles partner relationships. One contact who knows your agency, your clients, and your standard expectations. No call-centre handoffs, no rotating account managers.</p></div>
<div class="provide-card"><div><svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.7"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.25 15.75l5.159-5.159a2.25 2.25 0 013.182 0l5.159 5.159m-1.5-1.5l1.409-1.409a2.25 2.25 0 013.182 0l2.909 2.909m-18 3.75h16.5a1.5 1.5 0 001.5-1.5V6a1.5 1.5 0 00-1.5-1.5H3.75A1.5 1.5 0 002.25 6v12a1.5 1.5 0 001.5 1.5zm10.5-11.25h.008v.008h-.008V8.25zm.375 0a.375.375 0 11-.75 0 .375.375 0 01.75 0z"/></svg></div><h3>Marketing Assets Library</h3><p>Original photography from the mountain and northern Tanzania, video clips, route descriptions, packing lists, and brand-safe copy you can adapt for your site and client emails. Updated each season.</p></div>
<div class="provide-card"><div><svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.7"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 6v6h4.5m4.5 0a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg></div><h3>Real-Time Availability</h3><p>Honest answers on departure dates, route conditions, and capacity. We will tell you what is bookable today, what is filling fast, and which dates we are quietly recommending.</p></div>
<div class="provide-card"><div><svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.7"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.25 6.75c0 8.284 6.716 15 15 15h2.25a2.25 2.25 0 002.25-2.25v-1.372c0-.516-.351-.966-.852-1.091l-4.423-1.106c-.44-.11-.902.055-1.173.417l-.97 1.293c-.282.376-.769.542-1.21.38a12.035 12.035 0 01-7.143-7.143c-.162-.441.004-.928.38-1.21l1.293-.97c.363-.271.527-.734.417-1.173L6.963 3.102a1.125 1.125 0 00-1.091-.852H4.5A2.25 2.25 0 002.25 4.5v2.25z"/></svg></div><h3>On-Trip Support</h3><p>We handle every operational detail once your client lands: airport transfer, briefing, the climb itself, post-summit logistics, safari, Zanzibar. You receive trip updates so your client never feels handed off.</p></div>
<div class="provide-card"><div><svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.7"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75M21 12c0 1.268-.63 2.39-1.593 3.068a3.745 3.745 0 01-1.043 3.296 3.745 3.745 0 01-3.296 1.043A3.745 3.745 0 0112 21c-1.268 0-2.39-.63-3.068-1.593a3.746 3.746 0 01-3.296-1.043 3.745 3.745 0 01-1.043-3.296A3.745 3.745 0 013 12c0-1.268.63-2.39 1.593-3.068a3.745 3.745 0 011.043-3.296 3.745 3.745 0 013.296-1.043A3.745 3.745 0 0112 3c1.268 0 2.39.63 3.068 1.593a3.746 3.746 0 013.296 1.043 3.746 3.746 0 011.043 3.296A3.745 3.745 0 0121 12z"/></svg></div><h3>Insurance & Documentation</h3><p>Mandatory climber insurance verification, visa and vaccination guidance, documented porter welfare standards, full E-E-A-T documentation for any agency due diligence. We help you tick every compliance box.</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="who-section">
  <div class="container">
    <span class="section-eyebrow-center" style="color:var(--gold)">Who We Work With</span>
    <h2 class="section-title-center" style="color:#fff">Trusted by a Range of <em>Partners</em>.</h2>
    <p class="lead">From boutique agencies sending a few clients a year to adventure operators running full annual programmes, our partners look different but value the same things: reliability, margin, and a contact who answers the phone.</p>
    <div class="who-grid">
<div class="who-card"><h3>Travel Agencies</h3><p>Boutique agents and larger agencies wanting a reliable Tanzania programme. White-label or co-branded, your call.</p></div>
<div class="who-card"><h3>Adventure Tour Operators</h3><p>Adventure operators with Kilimanjaro in their catalogue who want a direct ground operator and stronger margins.</p></div>
<div class="who-card"><h3>University & College Programmes</h3><p>Outdoor programmes, study-abroad coordinators, and faculty-led expeditions. We have guided several family-style groups of climbers in their late teens to twenties with strong summit outcomes.</p></div>
<div class="who-card"><h3>Corporate Group Travel</h3><p>Leadership retreats, team-building expeditions, and incentive trips. Discreet handling, executive-level briefing, scaled crew, optional safari and Zanzibar extensions.</p></div>
<div class="who-card"><h3>Charity & Fundraising Climbs</h3><p>Charity climb organisers raising funds for causes. Per-climber pricing that lets your charity keep more of the fundraised total, plus group logistics support.</p></div>
<div class="who-card"><h3>Photographers & Filmmakers</h3><p>Professional film crews coordinating Tanzania Film Board permits, drone clearances, and high-altitude logistics. We have done the paperwork before.</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="how-section">
  <div class="container">
    <span class="section-eyebrow-center">How It Works</span>
    <h2 class="section-title-center">Four Steps to a <em>Live Partnership</em>.</h2>
    <p class="section-lead-center">We can be quoting your first enquiry within the same week. No drawn-out approval processes, no committee sign-off. A conversation, an agreement, and we start.</p>
    <div class="how-steps">
<div class="how-step"><div class="how-step-num">1</div><h3>Schedule a Call With Nelson</h3><p>Half an hour on Zoom or WhatsApp video. We learn about your agency, your clients, and the destinations you currently sell. You learn whether we are the right fit.</p></div>
<div class="how-step"><div class="how-step-num">2</div><h3>Sign a Simple Agreement</h3><p>Standard partner terms covering net rates, payment, cancellation policy, and operating standards. No exclusivity required, no annual minimums for new partners.</p></div>
<div class="how-step"><div class="how-step-num">3</div><h3>Start Quoting Your Clients</h3><p>We share marketing assets, current net rates, and quote turnaround commitments. You start sending us enquiries the same week.</p></div>
<div class="how-step"><div class="how-step-num">4</div><h3>We Run the Trip</h3><p>Once your client lands in Tanzania, the entire operation is on us. You stay informed by daily summary, your client experiences a seamless trip, and you receive the booking commission as agreed.</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="partner-faq">
  <div class="container">
    <span class="section-eyebrow-center">Partner FAQs</span>
    <h2 class="section-title-center">Common <em>Questions</em>.</h2>
    <p class="section-lead-center">Honest answers to the questions agencies ask before they sign. For anything not covered here, talk to Nelson directly.</p>
    <div class="dest-faq">
<details><summary>What net rates and commission structure do you offer?</summary><p>We discuss rates directly during the introductory call so we can match terms to your agency size, expected volume, and the types of climbs your clients book. Rates are tiered and improve with volume. The headline: there is real margin available for agency partners, and we keep our retail pricing honest so your clients are not getting a better deal direct.</p></details><details><summary>Is there an annual booking minimum?</summary><p>No annual minimum for new partners in the first year. After year one, we discuss expectations based on what is working for both sides. We would rather have ten committed partners than fifty inactive ones.</p></details><details><summary>Do you require exclusivity?</summary><p>No. We expect that you will have other ground operator relationships in other destinations, and possibly in Tanzania. We earn the booking with each enquiry, not by contract clause.</p></details><details><summary>How do you handle payment?</summary><p>Standard partner payment terms: deposit on confirmation, balance before arrival. We accept wire transfer, and we are exploring additional payment rails for partner convenience. Discussed in full at signing.</p></details><details><summary>Who is my point of contact?</summary><p>Nelson Mushi, owner and lead guide, handles partner relationships directly during the build phase. Once volume reaches a regular cadence, we may bring in a dedicated partner-operations contact, but Nelson stays accessible at all times.</p></details><details><summary>Can you support safari and Zanzibar extensions?</summary><p>Yes. Tanzania safaris across the Serengeti, Ngorongoro Crater, Tarangire, Lake Manyara, Arusha National Park, plus Zanzibar beach extensions are part of our standard offering. Many of our partner bookings combine Kilimanjaro with a safari and a few days at the coast. Single point of contact, single contract, single invoice.</p></details><details><summary>Do you provide white-label or co-branded materials?</summary><p>Yes, on request. We can supply route descriptions, photography, and itinerary templates branded for your agency. Discuss with Nelson at the introductory call.</p></details><details><summary>Where are you based and how do we reach you?</summary><p>Moshi, Tanzania, at the foot of Kilimanjaro. Reach Nelson at info@gokilimanjarotreks.com, +255 677 917 500, or WhatsApp at wa.me/255677917500. Time zone is East Africa Time (UTC+3), and we respond to partner emails outside business hours when needed.</p></details>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="cta-partner">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Let's Have a <em>Conversation</em>.</h2>
    <p>Half an hour, Zoom or WhatsApp video. Nelson will walk through how our programme fits your agency, what net rates look like at your projected volume, and what your first quote turnaround would feel like. No pitch deck, no sales process, no commitment.</p>
    <div class="cta-options">
      <a href="contact.html?subject=Partnership%20enquiry" class="btn-gold">Schedule a Call &#x2192;</a>
      <a href="mailto:info@gokilimanjarotreks.com?subject=Travel%20Agency%20Partnership" class="btn-line">&#x2709;&#xFE0F; Email Nelson</a>
      <a href="https://wa.me/255677917500?text=Hi%20Nelson%2C%20I%27d%20like%20to%20discuss%20a%20travel%20agency%20partnership." class="btn-line" target="_blank" rel="noopener">&#x1F4AC; WhatsApp Now</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
</main>

</BaseLayout>